long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
[For Internal usage only]

* This extension is designed only for SolarBK Internal usage. Please do not download if you're not in SolarBK.

SolarBK GAssistant Chrome Extension developed for SolarBK. This will help user unlock the Viewer right on Google Slides and block invalid download from SolarBK Drive.

- You can use this extension to unlock Viewer of Google Slides. Just fill the email and you can edit your Slides.

- This extension will also block invalid download if you make copy or download files illegally.
